name: The Magical Item #10: Waket: The Temple of Time
description: Dino and his crew reach the 10th Magical Location, The Temple of Time. In this place, the Time Beasts are created using the secret elixir found in the Magic Sauce Location. These beasts are heroes of this World and their role is to look after the Magical Items. This location can be seen as a checkpoint in space and time. Dino-sauce, the alter ego of Dino, living in a different dimension, gives him the power of time. Unlocking this portal will allow you to increase your Time Control by 700 MPs.
